data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2,165 square foot home boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a versatile study/office space and an inviting game room. The house equipped modern luxury with numerous upgrades including a beautiful renovated kitchen featuring cabinets and granite countertops, along with matching granite countertop in all bathrooms. Living area cozy up by the fireplace controlled by a convenient remote, surrounded by built in shelves and cabinets. Enjoying the expansive outdoors with huge extended covered patio, complete with all concrete flooring in the back yard perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Easy access to major highway 249 and 99 grand parkway. Additionally, it's zoned to AAA excellent school offering an exceptional educational experience for families. This home also offers the convenience of full-house water softener. Hurry and schedule a showing, it won't last!
